## `test_fuse_xattr_create_flag(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-fxattr-6 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: syscall boundary + errno mapping -->

### Postconditions

```python
path = mount / "f"
path.touch()

os.setxattr(path, "user.x", b"first")
with pytest.raises(FileExistsError) as e:
    os.setxattr(path, "user.x", b"second", flags=os.XATTR_CREATE)
assert e.value.errno == errno.EEXIST
```

---

